    <briefdescription>
<para>Reset Reason class implemented according to C++ singleton design pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The class provides methods to handle the reset reason, which is determined at startup by reading register RESETREAS. Register value and reset reason string are stored outside of this class in context of the caller of getter function. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
